data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful estate home is almost 3,100 sf and sits on half an acre lot, at the end of a cul-de-sac, with neighbors on only one side providing views and complete privacy. The formal entry opens to the living room with rich hardwood floors, custom built-in shelves, a gorgeous fireplace, cathedral ceilings, and a bay window filling up the space up with natural light. The kitchen with a bar isle is the hub of this special home and opens to the family room with another beautiful fireplace and a large glass slider out to the rear grounds, and on the other side opens to the formal dining room. The main level also offers a bedroom, a full bathroom, and the laundry room.  Upstairs leads to two large bedrooms with a second full bathroom, and the spacious master suite. The primary bedroom enjoys a balcony with a view of the backyard, a third full bath with a jacuzzi tub, a walk in closet, and an addition adding 400 sf of flex space you can use as a 5th bedroom, office, a nursery, or second closet. The yard has ample room for a pool or ADU! With a 3 car attached garage, recessed lighting throughout, no Mello roos, low HOA, and of course, the award-winning schools of this treasured neighborhood, we welcome you home!
